{"tid":340492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只有係球場先可以見到日本人醜陋一面","createTime":"2017-07-30T04:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T06:50:54.000Z","uid":51215,"like":71,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"202d7c4e2d4d0e034bece81252822dfca4131200","tid":340492,"uid":51215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:02:37.000Z","msg":"話說之前去大阪睇波，由於買唔到劃左位既波飛，我就買左兩張自由坐既波飛。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於之前係香港睇波早一個鍾都冇位既關係，我決定早兩個半鐘去坐低，諗住搵個好位置享受下。<br />\n<br />\n好啦咁我同朋友去到，係下面望上去個球場度見到冇乜人，加埋隔離有個牌寫住不准霸位，咁應該實有位坐，點知一路行上去見到啲空櫈全撚部都有啲毛巾呀 衫呀 袋呀霸撚住啲位。個一刻真係火都黎，明明有咁多告示牌叫你地唔好霸位，你班日本仔就全部霸撚哂啲位。<br />\n<br />\n不過比著係其他人種，我諗啲位都係會比人霸哂既，只不過原來被稱為好守規矩既日本人都會做啲咁既事。<br />\n<br />\n結論: 任何人係個人利益面前都係唔會讓步<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tb4zyjlo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftb4zyjlo&h=ce5a2f91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce7857920a4584d4d0c260631fa1afd67f741f16","tid":340492,"uid":56505,"like":5,"dislike":110,"score":-105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"你去人地方 跟返人地做法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3936b82ac94befbb2d4119e8c7bd2eb88600e2","tid":340492,"uid":82640,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你去人地方 跟返人地做法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188d540e6fc6c6ba7abe6809f2cb2c3e0998b61f","tid":340492,"uid":23021,"like":24,"dislike":43,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"中國人黎<br />\n日本人唔會咁"},{"pid":"3314ab4fc6d7761618f7e1a171ebe830c729e456","tid":340492,"uid":41846,"like":10,"dislike":26,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:13:38.000Z","msg":"唔準你咁話我哋偉大嘅日本國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定喺你睇錯"},{"pid":"25b0f90d022bacbe1fadf9c598404c266d7e8adb","tid":340492,"uid":29887,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"cite