/blockquote><br />\n我都好鐘意日本 但如果日本人唔守規矩就真係鐘意唔落<br />\n利申先: 球場外面既日本人係守規矩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69bc5bcc1d8704eeae02f996152e1cd8c7afc57","tid":340492,"uid":11694,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"條毛巾係俾你用ga"},{"pid":"6e519059bc1a06ca7cbfb6b88586ab759e19a5db","tid":340492,"uid":51215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條毛巾係俾你用ga</blockquote><br />\n我一入去都以為係 後尾我見到有人攤長條毛巾擺3 4 個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c48d6b9c06d6edc495fe3e800d4e20367521bf","tid":340492,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:28:19.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩啊 自己霸自己位不嬲得"},{"pid":"133245be3de9e8ec275793d05d993b892d132153","tid":340492,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:28:58.000Z","msg":"小日本到而加都忘記左打輸比中國既事<br />\n<br />\n武統日本"},{"pid":"b0fe4bb97f6aadf3430c8875ce180081d2cbfd66","tid":340492,"uid":51215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜鳩啊 自己霸自己位不嬲得</blockquote><br />\n啲人係霸比未到既 朋友坐的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c2c2ace8f5f9c8f70948233ccca2393112173e","tid":340492,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>條毛巾係俾你用ga</blockquote><br />\n我一入去都以為係 後尾我見到有人攤長條毛巾擺3 4 個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係俾你用ga，攞黎走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bac2e3a78bc5ab66041f8ff574c620a9b0f9f17","tid":340492,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條毛巾係俾你用ga</blockquote><br />\n我一入去都以為係 後尾我見到有人攤長條毛巾擺3 4 個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係俾你用ga，攞黎用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ad3e628cc6911f49b6472167059f8290da80b733","tid":340492,"uid":118314,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:04:45.000Z","msg":"想睇日本人醜陋一面其實唔難，去居酒屋<br />\n當你望住佢地一邊食野一邊扯煙，你就明白，<br />\n佢地其實並唔係有禮貌嘅民族，而係守規矩嘅民族。"},{"pid":"e9c5b017b6f8891cacbd111ee6a2a93a2ea7d865","tid":340492,"uid":21309,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇日本人醜陋一面其實唔難，去居酒屋<br />\n當你望住佢地一邊食野一邊扯煙，你就明白，<br />\n佢地其實並唔係有禮貌嘅民族，而係守規矩嘅民族。</blockquote><br />\n最弊我地兩樣都冇呢"},{"pid":"da64a571caa31c3835b7fcdbaeff4f2e76218000","tid":340492,"uid":91362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:39:50.000Z","msg":"日本人鍾意打假波<br />\n好嘔心"},{"pid":"929032ca3183f05cdcfd89290a4fe8d4b01b19be","tid":340492,"uid":14537,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:39:54.000Z","msg":"一有屌既日本po<br />\n就一定會有成堆支那狗扮崇日撚曲線引人屌日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcca1da8d99d92e8a68bdee3770d7fbbbad842d3","tid":340492,"uid":34256,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一有屌既日本po<br />\n就一定會有成堆支那狗扮崇日撚曲線引人屌日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真"},{"pid":"dd5705b600447bea9371a8f52a8346f54f9e1016","tid":340492,"uid":19501,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇日本人醜陋一面其實唔難，去居酒屋<br />\n當你望住佢地一邊食野一邊扯煙，你就明白，<br />\n佢地其實並唔係有禮貌嘅民族，而係守規矩嘅民族。</blockquote><br />\n部份居酒屋係寫明可以食煙架喎"},{"pid":"40122092140b068f7116c454c94906e0d743ad06","tid":340492,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"架佬成日話自己點好點有禮貌點乾淨<br />\n去完一次東京就完全真相大白<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acf68244fbc6e53515f9786ac236ab4679bcb0f","tid":340492,"uid":45353,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇日本人醜陋一面其實唔難，去居酒屋<br />\n當你望住佢地一邊食野一邊扯煙，你就明白，<br />\n佢地其實並唔係有禮貌嘅民族，而係守規矩嘅民族。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你又以偏概全<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉句講法日本鍾意有禮貌既民族<br />\n但樹大有枯支<br />\n所以要立規矩黎一致性風向<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日話戴面目壓抑<br />\n<br />\n但另一面又唔可以話無人鍾意互相尊重既文明社會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你d獨裁國家做唔到唔等於無"},{"pid":"d9d8dc1309b00fd80eaa2fd3ff192cf37a5bcbb0","tid":340492,"uid":9542,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"做旅客d 野可以見到幾多野？工作果d 先醜陋到仆街<br />\n<br />\nBtw 成日d 香港同支那覺得日本人完美，之後無啦啦有唔好感覺就好似夢想幻滅咁，唔好咁on撚9啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8d3ab0fc8485e783916b0c82ae8e2af087d5a8","tid":340492,"uid":4180,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一有屌既日本po<br />\n就一定會有成堆支那狗扮崇日撚曲線引人屌日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真</blockquote><br />\n難得終於有位入日本, 仲唔引仇恨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdfd557a1e84dcd3eb0226f12625bb8229c0a3b","tid":340492,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做旅客d 野可以見到幾多野？工作果d 先醜陋到仆街<br />\n<br />\nBtw 成日d 香港同支那覺得日本人完美，之後無啦啦有唔好感覺就好似夢想幻滅咁，唔好咁on撚9啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中曬，硬係有班人當日本人係聖人，睇日本人果時standard 高撚到，笑少下已經話下日本人啲禮貌呢乜乜乜，好撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83afa656fb3ff8ec2e0f3180f0f1e942f6df3127","tid":340492,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"想睇日本人點賤 打下fifa就知"},{"pid":"5a4f489611fc67cbde9c61bc831ff5daaa11167f","tid":340492,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇日本人點賤 打下fifa就知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打 fifa 點賤都唔夠韓狗嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本對比周圍垃圾國家，一定最高質，唔駛諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4572b9cc86530851445780a68dbc9ef34404cc08","tid":340492,"uid":65354,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"櫻花球迷不嬲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利: 飛腳球迷 有去睇derby<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d0e189a1919a0d388fdb1fac874e75e3d38c54","tid":340492,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"日本狗 祖國統治日倭不遠"},{"pid":"10b79148dee0336ebcc385174d4b5f15e2091ac0","tid":340492,"uid":25267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想睇日本人點賤 打下fifa就知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打 fifa 點賤都唔夠韓狗嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本對比周圍垃圾國家，一定最高質，唔駛諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本成個亞洲打fifa 都係西"},{"pid":"8393a45e4047de14d1cb811cb79294f6d28459c7","tid":340492,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:54:33.000Z","msg":"毛巾衫袋點反映一定係日本人 戇尻仔樓豬老屈都要醒小小"},{"pid":"fd88baf75fece431275c4a84da9b177f69b233e9","tid":340492,"uid":3713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:59:53.000Z","msg":"樓主作為中國人，先有呢種諗法！"},{"pid":"f9e53df1f7995a04c29640ac6ddd9a10cc8a56b4","tid":340492,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite